What:		/sys/bus/xen-backend/devices/*/state
Date:		August 2018
KernelVersion:	4.19
Contact:	Joe Jin <joe.jin@oracle.com>
Description:
                The state of the device. One of: 'Unknown',
                'Initialising', 'Initialised', 'Connected', 'Closing',
                'Closed', 'Reconfiguring', 'Reconfigured'.
